<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:11:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>秘鲁寻求避免对中国建造的大型港口进行仲裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/peru-seeks-avoid-arbitration-over-chinese-built-mega-port-2024-04-29/</link><description>一位官员周一表示，秘鲁政府正在寻求避免中国港口运营商中远海运可能就该公司正在建造的大型设施的排他权的法律纠纷提起的国际仲裁程序。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 19:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/peru-seeks-avoid-arbitration-over-chinese-built-mega-port-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>塑料谈判因产量限制陷入僵局而升温</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/plastic-treaty-talks-behind-schedule-amid-impasse-over-production-limits-2024-04-29/</link><description>由于世界对其第一个塑料条约应有多大的雄心仍存在分歧，各国正在考虑在 12 月达成预期协议之前召开一系列小型会议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 16:34:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/plastic-treaty-talks-behind-schedule-amid-impasse-over-production-limits-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>英国称到2025年将从敏感地点移除中国制造的监控套件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/chinese-made-surveillance-kit-be-removed-sensitive-sites-by-2025-says-uk-2024-04-29/</link><description>英国政府周一表示，由于对北京间谍活动的担忧日益加剧，英国希望在 2025 年 4 月之前从敏感地点移除中国制造的监控技术。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 14:49:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/chinese-made-surveillance-kit-be-removed-sensitive-sites-by-2025-says-uk-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪第一季度盈利疲弱，价格战显现影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-shows-effects-price-war-with-weaker-profit-growth-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国电动汽车 (EV) 制造商比亚迪周一公布了自 2022 年以来最弱的季度利润增长，同时，由于电动汽车需求放缓和全球最大汽车市场激烈的价格战，其收入增长放缓至近四年来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 11:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-shows-effects-price-war-with-weaker-profit-growth-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>尽管经济不景气，中国人在尿布和高露洁上的支出仍在增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-spend-more-diapers-colgate-despite-economic-woes-2024-04-29/</link><description>据尿布和一些高露洁牙膏制造商的高管称，中国消费者在尿布和一些高露洁牙膏上的支出有所增加，尽管消费者对中国的房地产危机和经济衰退感到担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 10:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-spend-more-diapers-colgate-despite-economic-woes-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：在美联储主导的忙碌的一周中，日元从 160 美元兑 160 美元反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-29/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 10:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>埃利奥特增持股份，英美资源集团面临压力，被迫披露抵御必和必拓的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bhp-adviser-canvassing-investor-views-improved-anglo-bid-sources-say-2024-04-29/</link><description>周一，英美资源集团面临股东的呼吁，要求详细制定提高其价值的计划，以抵御竞购者必和必拓，因为激进投资者埃利奥特通过增加其在收购目标中的持股进一步提高了股份。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 08:53:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bhp-adviser-canvassing-investor-views-improved-anglo-bid-sources-say-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>拜登签署台湾和TikTok立法后，中国暗示将进行报复</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-hints-retaliation-after-biden-signs-taiwan-tiktok-legislation-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国周一暗示，在美国总统乔·拜登签署加强台湾防御的法律并寻求让 TikTok 的中国所有者从该社交媒体平台撤资后，中国可能会进行报复。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 08:49:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-hints-retaliation-after-biden-signs-taiwan-tiktok-legislation-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国五巨头第一季度利润率缩水</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-agbank-posts-163-fall-q1-profit-2024-04-29/</link><description>由于银行面临支持现金匮乏的房地产开发商的压力，而贷款需求仍然疲软，中国五大银行的利润率在第一季度出现萎缩。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 08:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-agbank-posts-163-fall-q1-profit-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国将对美国部分产品的进口关税豁免期限延长至11月30日</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-extend-tariff-exemptions-imports-some-us-products-until-nov-30-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国财政部周一在一份声明中表示，中国将对部分美国产品的进口关税豁免期限延长至11月30日。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 08:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-extend-tariff-exemptions-imports-some-us-products-until-nov-30-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>什么是特斯拉的全自动驾驶以及为什么其在中国的推出很重要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/what-is-teslas-full-self-driving-why-its-china-rollout-matters-2024-04-29/</link><description>据知情人士透露，特斯拉首席执行官埃隆·马斯克周日抵达北京进行一次未经宣布的访问，预计他将讨论全自动驾驶（FSD）软件的推出以及向海外传输数据的许可。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 08:21:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/what-is-teslas-full-self-driving-why-its-china-rollout-matters-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平将访问法国、塞尔维亚和匈牙利，旨在促进欧盟关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-visit-france-serbia-hungary-may-5-10-foreign-ministry-says-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平将于5月5日至10日访问法国、塞尔维亚和匈牙利，这是他五年来的首次欧洲之行，旨在在与世界第二大经济体的紧张局势加剧之际促进欧盟关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 07:41:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-visit-france-serbia-hungary-may-5-10-foreign-ministry-says-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>农化公司先正达第一季度销售额和盈利大幅下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/agrochemicals-company-syngenta-posts-big-drop-q1-sales-earnings-2024-04-29/</link><description>种子和农药制造商先正达周一表示，第一季度销售额和利润大幅下降，就在这家瑞士公司搁置其 100 亿美元上市计划几周后。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 06:08:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/agrochemicals-company-syngenta-posts-big-drop-q1-sales-earnings-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国四月份工厂活动扩张速度可能放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-april-factory-activity-likely-expanded-slower-speed-2024-04-29/</link><description>路透社周一的一项调查显示，中国四月份的制造业活动可能会放缓，这表明该国庞大的工厂部门可能在第二季度初失去了一些动力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:49:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-april-factory-activity-likely-expanded-slower-speed-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产股因刺激计划而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-property-shares-rally-stimulus-hopes-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国房地产开发商的股价周一上涨，因市场猜测本周可能会出台更多刺激措施，旨在清理库存、促进销售和取消购房限制。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:47:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-property-shares-rally-stimulus-hopes-2024-04-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>